\q1 
\v 20 Ronampiri tajorentsiite, tzimatsiri ishintsinka, pithaamentee-yaari Tajorentsi!
\q1 Tema eerokaete antzirori okaatzi ikantzimiri.
\q1 Paamawentyaa, eero pipiyathatari rompera-tzimiri.
\v 21 Eerokaete maawoeni rowayirite, pikimo-shire-wenteeri Tajorentsi!
\q1 Eerokaete romperatani, panta-piinteeniri ikoyiri rirori!
\v 22 Eerokaete maawoeni rowetsikani Tajorentsi,
\q1 Pajahaa-wentee-yaari maawoeni jempe-rika-paeni ipinkathari-wentantzi!
\q1 Tema najahaa-wentari naaka Tajorentsi noshireki!
